data.description: 7.36 acres 921 feet  frontage on Alton St.  412ft  frontage on  Midas Spring.   Corner lot  Could be subdivided  Beautiful property with cleared acreage and mature hardwood forest.  33x 22 carport , 24 x 30 shop heated with wood stove with 220 and  water,  24 x 12 carport attached to shop, 28 x 25 patio with pergola,  large deck overlooks rear yard , covered front porch Home completed updated 2002  new roof,  gutters 2021 well pump and tank 2022. Set up to connect generator.  City water and sewer available.  Interesting history fact, see pictures of the Fountain of Youth on property built in the late 1800s . 20 minutes to Charlotte, Airport and Lake Norman  Convenient to Mountain Island Lake  and  Latta Park
